@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Dev token claims (use jwt.io with DEV signing key)
# {
#   "UserId": "4",
#   "DisplayName": "Trung Tam Chuyen Doi So",
#   "UnitId": "49",
#   "PhongBanId": "4",
#   "DeviceId": "test-device",
#   "Roles": ["CB.PCM", "LD.PCM"],
#   "UserIdUBTP": "123",
#   "PhongBanIdUBTP": "45",
#   "DonViIdUBTP": "78",
#   "iss": "mobile",
#   "aud": "mobile"
# }

### Auth/Me — with valid JWT Bearer token (generate using dev key)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ1234567890abcdefgh

###

### Auth/Me — without token → 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me

###
